title: Terakaft “Karambani” - Converse Red Light Session
description: The perfect mix of Terakaft’s deep bass tones, pulsating heartbeat of percussion, and two rhythm guitars—one keeping the beat effortlessly, the other soaring and sweet—transported this Converse Red Light Session to the deepest heart of the desert.
